Terms & Conditions:
 
1.Type of Prices: 
Price are Inclusive of Material + Transportation. And the materials shall be delivered/ dispatched strictly as per the instructions given in the Godrej Order.
 
2.Packing of Material:
Materials supplied against this order must be properly packed (confirming to special instructions and standard instructions for the materials) for safe transport by road or rail to the specified destination
 
3.Payment terms:
Supply Part:
100% payment with tax will be done within 45 days after receipt of material at site .
 
Installation & Commissioning:
100% payment with taxes after installation & commissioning within 45days after successful installation & commissioning at customers site and receipt of commissioning certificate from end user.
 
4.Delivery of Material: 
 
Supply & Manufacturing of  Roof Finalisation with template : 07th January  2021.
 
 
5.Progress of Fixture:
After placing of purchase order within a week period, Supplier shall submit a detailed activity-based timing plan starting from order receipt till equipment buy-off at 'Godrej', indicating the major milestones such as order receipt, DAP submission, DAP approval, procurement of bought outs, receipt of bought outs, drawing release for manufacturing, receipt of manufactured parts, sub-assemblies, major assemblies, readiness of equipment fully built ready condition or Supplier trials, if requirement of trial components, Supplier's own trials, Pre-dispatch inspection at Supplier etc.
 
6.Late Delivery (LD):
The agreed dates and delivery periods cannot be observed, for a reason which is attributable to the supplier, the Godrej is entitled to levy a contractual penalty of 0.5 % of the order value for each week or part week of delay, not exceeding 5 % of the scope of delivery to Synergytech Automation Pvt Ltd,.  which is in delay.
 
7.Warranty:
The Supplier fully guarantees the materials for a period of 24months from the date of acceptance of the material following all testing required by the Godrej or 18 months from delivery of the materials whichever comes earlier. Such warranty shall apply to any defect which may arise in the case of any of the materials attributable to faulty material, workmanship or design unless such design was carried out in detail by the Godrej.
 
8.Inspection of Materials:
All material will be inspected as per Godrej representative. And the Godrej shall have the right to inspect the materials during manufacture and before dispatch and to require such tests as may be called for in the order or any attached specification to be carried out to the Godrej satisfaction.
 
9.Installation & Commissioning:
Installation and commissioning will be done at Customer Site and application support will be provided as and when required.
 
10.Godrej will arrange the Unloading, Storage transfer at the site.
